	(77, NULL, 1, '3월 8일 심폐소생술(CPR)교육', '관리자', NULL, '<p><br></p><p><span style="color: rgb(38, 38, 38); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: normal;">지난 3월 8일 심폐소생술(CPR)교육이 있었습니다.</span><br style="color: rgb(38, 38, 38); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: normal;"><br style="color: rgb(38, 38, 38); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: normal;"><span style="color: rgb(38, 38, 38); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: normal;">이번 교육은 심폐소생술(CPR)과 자동심장충격기(AED) 사용법, 그리고 다양한 응급 상황에 빠르고 정확하게 대처하는 방법으로 진행되었습니다.</span><br style="color: rgb(38, 38, 38); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: normal;"><br style="color: rgb(38, 38, 38); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: normal;"><span style="color: rgb(38, 38, 38); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: normal;">메디인 병원은 주기적인 교육을 통해 모든직원이 응급상황에 신속하고 정확하게 대처할 수 있도록 다양한 프로그램을 진행할 예정입니다.</span></p><p><span style="color: rgb(38, 38, 38); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: normal;"><br></span></p><p><span style="color: rgb(38, 38, 38); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: normal;"><br></span></p><p><img src="/uploads/editor/d6477459a200802c7db9a756a524b636.jpg" data-filename="심폐소생술2.jpg" style="width: 800px;"></p><p><br></p><p><img src="/uploads/editor/119f0df50e8069c191e70fb7086e5574.jpg" data-filename="심폐소생술3.jpg" style="width: 800px;"></p><p><br></p><p><img src="/uploads/editor/bb0311581fbcb9022c53ea31dbe671e0.jpg" data-filename="심폐소생술1.jpg" style="width: 800px;"><span style="color: rgb(38, 38, 38); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: normal;"><br></span><br style="color: rgb(38, 38, 38); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: normal;"></p>', 3425, '112.161.27.82', 0, 0, 0, NULL, '2023-03-16 17:44:39', '2023-03-16 17:44:39', NULL, NULL, 'N', NULL, 'N', 'admin', 'admin', NULL, NULL, NULL, 'GN06000000', 'Y', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '', '', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 1);
