e="인공관절14.jpg" style="width: 800px;"></p><p><br></p><p><br></p><p><img src="/uploads/editor/08414d3752f41ae283a521f578a734c6.jpg" data-filename="인공관절15.jpg" style="width: 800px;"><br></p>', 1590, '112.161.27.82', 0, 0, 0, NULL, '2023-04-06 15:43:02', '2023-04-06 15:44:37', NULL, NULL, 'N', NULL, 'N', 'admin', 'admin', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Y', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '', '', 'FID00000033', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 1);
