	(83, NULL, 1, '나트륨 저감화 캠페인 \'싱나요\'', '관리자', NULL, '<p><br></p><p><span style="font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: normal;">지난 4월 13일 점심시간을 이용하여 나트륨 저감화 캠페인 \'싱나요\'가 진행되었습니다.</span><br style="font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: normal;"><br style="font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: normal;"><span style="font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: normal;">파주보건소와 함께한 이번 프로그램은</span><br style="font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: normal;"></p><p><br></p><p><span style="font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: normal;">1) 올바른 식습관 교육 및 홍보</span></p><p><span style="font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: normal;">2) 음식별 나트륨 비교 모형 전시</span><br style="font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: normal;"></p><p><span style="font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: normal;">3) 저염쿠키 비교 시식</span><br style="font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: normal;"></p><p><span style="font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: normal;">4) 나트륨 저감화 홍보 리플렛 제공 순으로 진행되었습니다.</span><br style="font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: normal;"><span style="font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: normal;">마지막으로 깜찍한 기념품까지~^^</span><br style="font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: normal;"><br style="font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: normal;"><span style="font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: normal;">바쁘신 와중에 함께해주신 파주보건소 직원 여러분 감사합니다~</span></p><p><span style="font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: normal;">메디인 가족 여러분~~</span></p><p><span style="font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: normal;">모두들 씽나는 하루 보내세요~~~♥</span><br></p><p><br></p><p><img src="/uploads/editor/991e1eafc55ca5cdf7cdc828bf95beb2.jpg" data-filename="싱나요1.jpg" style="font-size: 13px; letter-spacing: -0.26px; width: 800px;"><br></p><p><br></p><p><img src="/uploads/editor/ad1d8fc3917d07330dc8a062f0e92d94.jpg" data-filename="싱나요2.jpg" style="width: 800px;"></p><p><br></p><p><img src="/uploads/editor/9d68d55bfca499a02a88727601ae3fab.jpg" data-filename="싱나요4.jpg" style="width: 800px;"></p><p><br></p><p><img src="/uploads/editor/5f0a2ba38cb806caa3205a6c21e9c0d4.jpg" data-filename="싱나요3.jpg" style="width: 800px;"></p><p><br></p><p><br></p><p><br></p><p><img src="/uploads/editor/f02ee14653e3fe3d95585f1346960809.jpg" data-filename="싱나요5.jpg" style="width: 800px;"><br></p>', 3157, '112.161.27.82', 0, 0, 0, NULL, '2023-04-17 12:00:29', '2023-04-17 12:00:29', NULL, NULL, 'N', NULL, 'N', 'admin', 'admin', NULL, NULL, NULL, 'GN06000000', 'Y', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '', '', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 1);
