	(116, NULL, 1, '(주)알라딘커뮤니케이션 업무협약', '관리자', NULL, '<p><br></p><p><br></p><p>금일(6월16일) 메디인병원과 (주)알라딘커뮤니케이션과 업무협약이 진행되었습니다. </p><p><br></p><p><span style="font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-variant-alternates: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 14px; line-height: inherit; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, " segoe="" ui",="" roboto,="" helvetica,="" arial,="" sans-serif;="" flex-shrink:="" 0;="" letter-spacing:="" normal;"="">이번 협약을 통해 <span style="font-family: NanumGothic, sans-serif; font-size: 13px; letter-spacing: -0.26px;">(주)알라딘커뮤니케이션 직원여러분들에게</span> 최상의 의료서비스를 제공과 함께 주기적인 교류를 통해 다양한 프로그램을 진행할 예정입니다.</span><br style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-variant-alternates: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 14px; line-height: inherit; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, " segoe="" ui",="" roboto,="" helvetica,="" arial,="" sans-serif;="" flex-shrink:="" 0;="" letter-spacing:="" normal;"=""></p><p><br></p><p><br></p><p><img src="/uploads/editor/f0c87ed77d8403b8188f7188091e9bb6.jpg" data-filename="알라딘1.jpg" style="width: 50%;"><br></p>', 4870, '112.161.27.82', 0, 0, 0, NULL, '2023-06-16 17:11:42', '2023-06-28 16:54:26', NULL, NULL, 'N', NULL, 'N', 'admin', 'admin', NULL, NULL, NULL, 'GN06000000', 'Y', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '', '', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 1);
