	(225, NULL, 1, '⭐배우 김현규님이 드라마 촬영차 메디인병원을 방문하셨습니다.', '관리자', NULL, '<p><img src="/uploads/editor/d3704d19741b4479c6ed66f5ea7f8475.jpg" data-filename="신병성윤모.jpg" style="width: 800px;"></p><p><br></p><p><span style="font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, "Segoe UI", Roboto, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: normal;">Genie TV의 오리지널 콘텐츠 시리즈 <신병>에 출연하신 ⭐배우 김현규님이</span><br style="font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, "Segoe UI", Roboto, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: normal;"><span style="font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, "Segoe UI", Roboto, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: normal;">드라마 촬영차 메디인병원을 방문하셨습니다.</span><br style="font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, "Segoe UI", Roboto, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: normal;"><br style="font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, "Segoe UI", Roboto, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: normal;"><span style="font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, "Segoe UI", Roboto, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: normal;">연기도 잘하시고 성격도 너무너무 좋으신 배우 김현규님의 멋진 활동을 응원합니다~❤️</span><br style="font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, "Segoe UI", Roboto, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: normal;"><br></p>', 3506, '112.161.27.82', 0, 0, 0, NULL, '2024-03-19 13:21:00', '2024-03-26 17:39:08', NULL, NULL, 'N', NULL, 'N', 'admin', 'admin', NULL, NULL, NULL, 'GN06000000', 'Y', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '', '', 'FID00000196', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 1);
