	(241, NULL, 1, '정확하고 올바른 투약을 위한 환자안전 캠페인', '관리자', NULL, '<p><br></p><p><span style="font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, "Segoe UI", Roboto, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: normal;">지난 16일 정확하고 올바른 투약을 위한 환자안전 캠페인이 진행되었습니다.</span><br style="font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, "Segoe UI", Roboto, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: normal;"><br style="font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, "Segoe UI", Roboto, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: normal;"><span style="font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, "Segoe UI", Roboto, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: normal;">파주 최초 민간 종합병원 메디인병원은 대학병원급 첨단 장비를 이용한 수준 높은 의료 서비스를 제공합니다.</span><br style="font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, "Segoe UI", Roboto, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: normal;"><br style="font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, "Segoe UI", Roboto, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: normal;"><br></p><p><img src="/uploads/editor/0fc5bec1ad635f5bbe772ff753049e71.jpg" data-filename="5.16 환자안전캠페인1.jpg" style="width: 800px;"></p><p><br></p><p><img src="/uploads/editor/5a49f644799142128ec29298a3c376f7.jpg" data-filename="5.16 환자안전캠페인2.jpg" style="width: 800px;"></p><p><br></p><p><img src="/uploads/editor/46c4d30bc1046a2aa47e1acb97244319.jpg" data-filename="5.16 환자안전캠페인3.jpg" style="width: 800px;"></p><p><br></p><p><img src="/uploads/editor/c94e6a11f827a5653b48cb736a39214d.jpg" data-filename="5.16 환자안전캠페인4.jpg" style="width: 800px;"></p><p><br></p><p><img src="/uploads/editor/757eab0ab0e2ee050589b0466c570c25.jpg" data-filename="5.16 환자안전캠페인5.jpg" style="width: 800px;"></p><p><br></p><p><img src="/uploads/editor/65c4b52aab9f0c799383a28d3f328f91.jpg" data-filename="5.16 환자안전캠페인6.jpg" style="width: 800px;"></p><p><br></p><p><img src="/uploads/editor/087504c16c79d56f3d85061b6a813bb5.jpg" da